[
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=3"
  },
  {
    "text": "Hello! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=9"
  },
  {
    "text": "My name is Russell, and I'm an engineer on the UIKit team. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=11"
  },
  {
    "text": "In iOS 13, we introduced a refined appearance for sheets, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=14"
  },
  {
    "text": "bringing them to Phone ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=18"
  },
  {
    "text": "and adding a universal pull-to-dismiss gesture. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=20"
  },
  {
    "text": "To learn more about this, watch the video ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=23"
  },
  {
    "text": "Modernizing Your UI for iOS 13, specifically the section about ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=25"
  },
  {
    "text": "Presentations starting 9 minutes and 45 seconds in. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=30"
  },
  {
    "text": "In iOS 15, we've built on that foundation ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=33"
  },
  {
    "text": "by adding a bunch of customization options to sheets, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=37"
  },
  {
    "text": "so you can now use them in fun new ways like never before. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=40"
  },
  {
    "text": "We've added support for a medium detent, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=43"
  },
  {
    "text": "which allows you to create a vertically resizable sheet ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=45"
  },
  {
    "text": "that only covers half the screen.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=48"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can also now remove the dimming view, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=52"
  },
  {
    "text": "which will allow you to build a nonmodal UI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=54"
  },
  {
    "text": "where the user can interact with content behind the sheet ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=56"
  },
  {
    "text": "while the sheet is presented. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=59"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, I'll cover some new visual options, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=62"
  },
  {
    "text": "including how to get a non-full-screen appearance ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=64"
  },
  {
    "text": "on phones in landscape. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=67"
  },
  {
    "text": "And finally, I'll show how to set up a UI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=70"
  },
  {
    "text": "that seamlessly adapts between a popover ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=72"
  },
  {
    "text": "in regular size classes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=74"
  },
  {
    "text": "and a customized sheet in compact size classes.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=76"
  },
  {
    "text": "To explore all of this, we've made a sample app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=80"
  },
  {
    "text": "for creating digital postcards, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=82"
  },
  {
    "text": "and it's available with this video. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=84"
  },
  {
    "text": "For each postcard, I can customize the picture ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=86"
  },
  {
    "text": "as well as the text and the font. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=89"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, before I can customize a sheet, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=92"
  },
  {
    "text": "first I have to get one. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=94"
  },
  {
    "text": "A sheet is an instance of a new ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=96"
  },
  {
    "text": "UIPresentationController subclass ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=98"
  },
  {
    "text": "called UISheetPresentationController, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=100"
  },
  {
    "text": "and all of the customization options are exposed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=103"
  },
  {
    "text": "as properties on this class. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=105"
  },
  {
    "text": "The typical way to get an instance of this class ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=108"
  },
  {
    "text": "is to read ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=110"
  },
  {
    "text": "the sheetPresentationController property ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=111"
  },
  {
    "text": "on a view controller before you present it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=113"
  },
  {
    "text": "This method returns a non-nil instance ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=116"
  },
  {
    "text": "as long the view controller's modalPresentationStyle ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=118"
  },
  {
    "text": "is form sheet or page sheet, which it is by default.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=121"
  },
  {
    "text": "From here, you can then set ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=126"
  },
  {
    "text": "various properties on the instance to customize it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=127"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is the same pattern as getting a view controller's ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=130"
  },
  {
    "text": "popoverPresentationController and setting its properties. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=132"
  },
  {
    "text": "And with that, let's jump into detents.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=136"
  },
  {
    "text": "What are detents? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=141"
  },
  {
    "text": "A detent is a height where a sheet naturally rests, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=143"
  },
  {
    "text": "and these are defined as a fraction ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=148"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the fully expanded sheet frame. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=149"
  },
  {
    "text": "The fully expanded frame is visualized ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=152"
  },
  {
    "text": "on an iPhone and iPad here, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=154"
  },
  {
    "text": "and it should be familiar if you've used sheets before. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=156"
  },
  {
    "text": "We've exposed two system-defined detents in iOS 15: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=159"
  },
  {
    "text": "a medium detent, which is about half ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=163"
  },
  {
    "text": "of a sheet's full height, and a large detent, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=165"
  },
  {
    "text": "which is the height of a fully expanded sheet.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=167"
  },
  {
    "text": "To specify which detents you want a sheet to support, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=171"
  },
  {
    "text": "simply set an array of the detents you want ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=174"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the detents property. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=177"
  },
  {
    "text": "The default value of this property is an array ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=178"
  },
  {
    "text": "of just the large detent, which is why if you don't ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=180"
  },
  {
    "text": "set it at all, you get a standard full height sheet.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=183"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you set this to an array of the medium and large detents, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=189"
  },
  {
    "text": "you get a sheet that is resizable ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=192"
  },
  {
    "text": "between medium and large. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=194"
  },
  {
    "text": "But you can also set this to an array ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=197"
  },
  {
    "text": "of just the medium detent, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=199"
  },
  {
    "text": "which gives you a sheet that presents at medium height ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=201"
  },
  {
    "text": "and cannot be resized to full height. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=203"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's apply this to the sample app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=207"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm starting with some code that targets the iOS 14 SDK ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=209"
  },
  {
    "text": "to present the system image picker in a standard sheet. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=213"
  },
  {
    "text": "When a button is tapped, this first function is called, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=216"
  },
  {
    "text": "which creates an image picker, sets the picker's delegate ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=219"
  },
  {
    "text": "to self, and then presents the picker.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=222"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then when an image is chosen, the picker didFinishPicking ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=226"
  },
  {
    "text": "delegate method is called, which then sets the chosen image ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=229"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the image view and dismisses the picker.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=232"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's run it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=237"
  },
  {
    "text": "When I tap the photo button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=238"
  },
  {
    "text": "the photo picker covers the whole app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=240"
  },
  {
    "text": "Notice my traveling has recently been very virtual. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=242"
  },
  {
    "text": "And when I pick a photo, the photo picker dismisses, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=245"
  },
  {
    "text": "revealing the photo I picked in the postcard. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=248"
  },
  {
    "text": "But what if I want to pick a different picture? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=251"
  },
  {
    "text": "I have to go through this whole flow again. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=254"
  },
  {
    "text": "And it would be really nice if I could show ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=256"
  },
  {
    "text": "my library of photos and my postcard ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=257"
  },
  {
    "text": "at the same time. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=259"
  },
  {
    "text": "And with a medium detent, I can.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=261"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's the same code as before but with a few changes. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=264"
  },
  {
    "text": "Before I present the picker, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=268"
  },
  {
    "text": "I access its sheetPresentationController ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=269"
  },
  {
    "text": "and set its detents to medium and large. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=272"
  },
  {
    "text": "Also in the picker didFinishPicking ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=275"
  },
  {
    "text": "delegate callback, I removed the line ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=277"
  },
  {
    "text": "that dismisses the photo picker, because now I don't want ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=280"
  },
  {
    "text": "the photo picker to dismiss when selecting a picture.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=282"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now when I run this and tap the photo button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=286"
  },
  {
    "text": "my library comes up at half height, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=289"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can pick a photo, and voila. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=291"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can see it in my postcard with the library still below. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=294"
  },
  {
    "text": "And if I want to try a different photo, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=297"
  },
  {
    "text": "it's as simple as one tap. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=299"
  },
  {
    "text": "Also, because my detents array includes the large detent, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=302"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can drag the bar to resize this sheet to full height.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=305"
  },
  {
    "text": "In addition, because the scroll view ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=310"
  },
  {
    "text": "is scrolled to top, scrolling the scroll view ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=312"
  },
  {
    "text": "will also expand the sheet. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=314"
  },
  {
    "text": "For a sheet of actions like the system Share Sheet, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=316"
  },
  {
    "text": "this is a great feature that progressively discloses ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=318"
  },
  {
    "text": "more advanced actions at the bottom of the list. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=321"
  },
  {
    "text": "But for this photo library example, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=323"
  },
  {
    "text": "I might prefer that scrolling not expand the sheet ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=326"
  },
  {
    "text": "so the postcard is always visible ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=328"
  },
  {
    "text": "unless I explicitly resize the sheet ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=330"
  },
  {
    "text": "by dragging from the bar. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=332"
  },
  {
    "text": "To get this alternate behavior, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=334"
  },
  {
    "text": "I just have to set one additional property: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=336"
  },
  {
    "text": "PrefersScrollingExpands- WhenScrolledToEdge. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=339"
  },
  {
    "text": "By default, this property is true, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=343"
  },
  {
    "text": "so setting it to false prevents scrolling ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=345"
  },
  {
    "text": "from expanding the sheet.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=347"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now the photo picker doesn't resize when scrolled, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=350"
  },
  {
    "text": "but I can still drag the bar ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=353"
  },
  {
    "text": "to get a better view of my photo library.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=355"
  },
  {
    "text": "But now when I tap a photo, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=359"
  },
  {
    "text": "it's not obvious that anything happened. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=361"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is in contrast to the earlier behavior, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=364"
  },
  {
    "text": "where tapping a photo dismissed the photo picker, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=366"
  },
  {
    "text": "clearly indicating my selection was received.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=368"
  },
  {
    "text": "What I'd like is to have the sheet resize ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=372"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the medium detent when I tap a photo, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=374"
  },
  {
    "text": "both to indicate my selection was received ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=376"
  },
  {
    "text": "and to make my selection visible in the postcard. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=378"
  },
  {
    "text": "And I can achieve this by programmatically changing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=381"
  },
  {
    "text": "the selected detent. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=383"
  },
  {
    "text": "So if I go back to the image picker delegate method ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=386"
  },
  {
    "text": "that is called whenever a photo is tapped, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=388"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can add some code here to get the sheetPresentationController ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=390"
  },
  {
    "text": "and set the selectedDetentIdentifier ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=393"
  },
  {
    "text": "to medium. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=396"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's try this. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=397"
  },
  {
    "text": "Notice the transition when I tap a photo.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=399"
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=404"
  },
  {
    "text": "That transition was so fast, I almost lost my eyebrows. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=405"
  },
  {
    "text": "It actually didn't animate at all. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=408"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can easily animate this transition ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=410"
  },
  {
    "text": "by wrapping the setting of the property ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=412"
  },
  {
    "text": "in a sheet.animateChanges block. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=414"
  },
  {
    "text": "This will animate the sheet down to the medium detent if needed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=416"
  },
  {
    "text": "with a standard animation curve ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=419"
  },
  {
    "text": "and animate other sheets in the stack as well, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=421"
  },
  {
    "text": "such as the root sheet scaling back up.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=423"
  },
  {
    "text": "Buttery smooth. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=430"
  },
  {
    "text": "One more nice thing would be to remove the dimming view ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=432"
  },
  {
    "text": "to show the selected photo in full color. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=435"
  },
  {
    "text": "To do that, there's one more property to look at ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=438"
  },
  {
    "text": "called smallestUndimmed- DetentIdentifier. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=441"
  },
  {
    "text": "By default, this property is nil, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=444"
  },
  {
    "text": "which means all of the detents are dimmed, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=446"
  },
  {
    "text": "but if you want to remove dimming, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=448"
  },
  {
    "text": "set it to the identifier of the smallest detent ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=450"
  },
  {
    "text": "where you don't want dimming. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=452"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this case, I'll set it to medium.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=453"
  },
  {
    "text": "Notice there's no dimming at the medium detent ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=457"
  },
  {
    "text": "when I bring up the picker. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=459"
  },
  {
    "text": "Ta-da! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=462"
  },
  {
    "text": "But dimming still fades in if I resize to the large detent.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=463"
  },
  {
    "text": "More than visually removing the dimming, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=468"
  },
  {
    "text": "this property also allows you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=470"
  },
  {
    "text": "to build advanced nonmodal experiences, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=472"
  },
  {
    "text": "since I can now interact ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=474"
  },
  {
    "text": "not only with the content in the sheet ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=476"
  },
  {
    "text": "but also with the content outside of the sheet.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=478"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is even more profound with the font picker, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=482"
  },
  {
    "text": "where I've built a UI that allows me to select ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=485"
  },
  {
    "text": "a range of text while the font picker is up, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=487"
  },
  {
    "text": "apply a font to just that range, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=490"
  },
  {
    "text": "adjust my selection, and apply a font again. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=492"
  },
  {
    "text": "Download the sample app for details on how this is achieved.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=495"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's also worth noting that medium height sheets ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=500"
  },
  {
    "text": "support automatic keyboard avoidance, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=502"
  },
  {
    "text": "so if I search for a font here, the sheet grows automatically ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=505"
  },
  {
    "text": "to account for the keyboard, and when the keyboard dismisses, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=508"
  },
  {
    "text": "the sheet automatically collapses back down.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=511"
  },
  {
    "text": "So that was a lot of information about detents, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=515"
  },
  {
    "text": "but now I'd like to turn our attention ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=518"
  },
  {
    "text": "to some other new visual customization options ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=520"
  },
  {
    "text": "for sheets, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=522"
  },
  {
    "text": "starting with a new optional appearance for sheets ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=524"
  },
  {
    "text": "on iPhone in landscape. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=526"
  },
  {
    "text": "In iOS 13, we made all sheets full screen in landscape, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=528"
  },
  {
    "text": "and now we've made available an alternate appearance ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=532"
  },
  {
    "text": "where sheets are only attached to the screen ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=535"
  },
  {
    "text": "at their bottom edge.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=537"
  },
  {
    "text": "To get this new appearance, simply set ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=540"
  },
  {
    "text": "prefersEdgeAttached- InCompactHeight to true. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=542"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now just setting this will always give you a sheet ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=546"
  },
  {
    "text": "that is as wide as the safe area. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=548"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you'd like a sheet whose width follows ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=550"
  },
  {
    "text": "the presentedViewControllers preferredContentSize, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=552"
  },
  {
    "text": "set widthFollows- PreferredContentSize- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=555"
  },
  {
    "text": "WhenEdgeAttached to true. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=557"
  },
  {
    "text": "This will make the sheet a narrower default width, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=559"
  },
  {
    "text": "and you can set preferredContentSize ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=562"
  },
  {
    "text": "to further customize this width. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=563"
  },
  {
    "text": "Besides these properties, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=567"
  },
  {
    "text": "there is also a property to show a grabber if you like. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=568"
  },
  {
    "text": "A grabber often isn't necessary, but in cases ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=571"
  },
  {
    "text": "where it might be less obvious that a sheet is resizable, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=573"
  },
  {
    "text": "such as when scrolling doesn't resize the sheet, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=576"
  },
  {
    "text": "displaying the grabber can be a helpful indicator ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=578"
  },
  {
    "text": "of resizability. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=581"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now notice the corners of the sheet. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=583"
  },
  {
    "text": "Another option we've exposed is the ability ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=586"
  },
  {
    "text": "to customize the corner radius. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=588"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your app has a more rounded appearance, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=590"
  },
  {
    "text": "you may want to match that aesthetic. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=593"
  },
  {
    "text": "Note that the system will keep stacked corners ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=595"
  },
  {
    "text": "looking consistent, so if this photo picker expands ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=597"
  },
  {
    "text": "to push back the root sheet, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=600"
  },
  {
    "text": "the root sheet will have larger corners to match. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=602"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, although it's possible to create a sheet ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=605"
  },
  {
    "text": "with detents on iPad, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=607"
  },
  {
    "text": "often a popover is wanted instead ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=609"
  },
  {
    "text": "that adapts to a sheet in compact, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=611"
  },
  {
    "text": "potentially customized with things like detents. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=613"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's take this approach with the sample app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=616"
  },
  {
    "text": "To get a popover for the image picker on iPad, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=619"
  },
  {
    "text": "I need to make a few small modifications. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=622"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, I'll set the modalPresentationStyle ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=624"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the picker to popover. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=627"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, instead of grabbing the sheetPresentationController, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=629"
  },
  {
    "text": "because this will now return nil, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=632"
  },
  {
    "text": "since the modalPresentationStyle is not a sheet, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=634"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll get the popoverPresentationController. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=636"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll set the popover's source to be our barButtonItem, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=640"
  },
  {
    "text": "and then I'll grab a new property on the popover ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=643"
  },
  {
    "text": "called the adaptiveSheet- PresentationController. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=645"
  },
  {
    "text": "This property returns an instance of the sheet ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=648"
  },
  {
    "text": "that the popover will adapt to in compact size classes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=650"
  },
  {
    "text": "and then I'll configure it just as I did the sheet before.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=654"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now when I tap a photo button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=659"
  },
  {
    "text": "the photo picker appears in the popover, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=661"
  },
  {
    "text": "and if I resize the scene, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=663"
  },
  {
    "text": "it adapts to a medium height sheet. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=665"
  },
  {
    "text": "It works! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=667"
  },
  {
    "text": "And if I expand the picker, and select a photo-- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=669"
  },
  {
    "text": "oh, no! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=672"
  },
  {
    "text": "It didn't automatically resize to medium height ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=674"
  },
  {
    "text": "like we implemented before. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=676"
  },
  {
    "text": "Hmm. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=678"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's go back to the picker ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=679"
  },
  {
    "text": "didFinishPicking delegate method.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=680"
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=683"
  },
  {
    "text": "To get the adaptive sheet, I need to read ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=684"
  },
  {
    "text": "the adaptiveSheet- PresentationController ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=686"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the popoverPresentationController ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=688"
  },
  {
    "text": "here in the code as well. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=690"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now notice when I select a photo. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=693"
  },
  {
    "text": "Hooray! It resizes back to medium again.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=696"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, I've talked about a lot of stuff here ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=701"
  },
  {
    "text": "that will enable you to easily build new types of UIs ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=704"
  },
  {
    "text": "with sheets that could not be easily built before. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=706"
  },
  {
    "text": "Review your own apps for areas that would benefit ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=710"
  },
  {
    "text": "from medium height sheets or nonmodal experiences. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=712"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you have any half height custom cards in your apps today, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=716"
  },
  {
    "text": "replace them with these newly enhanced UIKit sheets. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=719"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you for watching, and I look forward to seeing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=722"
  },
  {
    "text": "all of the cool new things\nyou build with sheets.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10063/?time=724"
  }
]